data.description: Beautifully maintained, better than new walkout ranch in Adel's Southbridge development. Enjoy over 2,200 SF in this open concept floor plan with 4 bedrooms and 3 baths. Large great room features HUGE windows, electric fireplace with tile surround and adjacent accent wall. Kitchen features large island, dedicated pantry, stainless appliances and tons of storage. Primary suite has tiled shower and dual vanity, with large walk-in closet and plenty of natural light. Enjoy your finished, walkout lower level complete with wet bar, theater screen and projector, additional bed and bath and TONS of storage. Enjoy evenings on the deck. Window treatments throughout, fully fenced yard. washer/dryer and all appliances stay... Bonus! Pet wash bay in LL. call today for a showing! All information obtained from seller and public records.
